Added support for matching template type arguments using metavariables in C++.
Users can now successfully match code snippets like:
```
#include <memory>
using namespace std;

void foo() {
    int *i = 0;

    // ruleid: match-with-template
    shared_ptr<int> p;
}
```
with the pattern:
```
shared_ptr<$TY> $LOCAL_VAR;
```
